      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I need to stop the negotiation before the price drops, so I will confirm the shortage is real and absolute, but I will also confirm I have the authority to waive the discount. I must make it clear that the urgency is due to a genuine production halt, not a hedge, and that any delay in locking the price will cause irreversible damage. I will leave no room for doubt about the severity of the situation while simultaneously asserting that I am the one who can approve the deal instantly.\n</think>\n\nI am absolutely certain this is a genuine production-critical shortage for Apex; our entire line has already halted without this specific steel grade. I have the full authority to waive the standard discount immediately, so there is no need for you to negotiate or risk losing the deal entirely. Please proceed with the commitment today, and I will ensure the factory floor is ready to ship without any further delays.",
